    "type": "message",
    "text": "I'm so happy to hear someone else use that term. That's exactly what I've been calling myself. It seems to be a reoccurring theme here - Being tired of waiting for some existing organization to do something official and just going at it on your own. It's inspiring to see others do this. What a great time to be alive to do this. We already own all of our equipment, software and reading material as essentially free, colleagues are everyone around the world available for collaboration. And all it costs is your time.",
